EEEEDDDDIIIITTTTIIIINNNNGGGG
     The application provides  an edition area with text  window,
     menubar, scrollbar and control-panel for commands line, mes-
     sages window and buttons. If a text window  has  the  focus,
     the  caracters  typed  are  insered  at the current position
     (cursor) .
     Six buttons are used to move through the buffer  (top,  bot-
     tom,  smooth  scroll  up  and down, previous and next page).
     Mouse button1 (left)  can be use to move the cursor  in  the
     current page.
     During a session, several edition areas can be used  (Max  :
     16).  A new edition area is opened with 'New text window' in
     Window menu. Each of them inherites of the current directory
     of  its  parent.  The  first  window has the current working
     directory.  The directory of a text window is  that  of  the
     loaded file.

