     XCORAL_TAB_WIDTH is used to set tab width. Default is  stan-
     dard width tab.
     XCORAL_INDENT_WIDTH is used in C or C++  mode  to  set  auto
     indent width.  Default is 3 blanks and -1 for tab.
     XCORAL_VISIT_RAISE is used in browser to raise  or  not  the
     visit  window  during  a  select operation. Default is True.
     XCORAL_PARSE_FILES_AT_STARTUP is used at start-up  to  parse
